        "MasterPrompt":  "MAIN_TITLE_TH: เสน่ห์ร่มบ่อสร้างSUB_TITLE_TH: หัตถศิลป์ล้านนาMAIN_TITLE_EN: BO SANG UMBRELLASUB_TITLE_EN: Lanna Craft CollectionCENTER_OBJECT: A handcrafted Bo Sang umbrella with a bamboo frame and hand-painted floral patterns, partially open and placed in a woven basket with natural materials.ARCH_STYLE: Traditional Lanna wooden veranda arch with carved floral motifs and teak pillars.GARDEN_VIEW: A peaceful Northern Thai village garden with paper umbrella workshops, flowering plants, and soft sunlight filtering through trees.COLOR_PALETTE: Soft Sky Blue, Natural Bamboo Beige, Crimson Red, Leaf Green, Warm White.### [MASTER PROMPT — THAI VINTAGE FRAME ILLUSTRATION V.2 (THAI PRIORITY)]TASK: Create a symmetrical, elegant vintage Thai illustration featuring an architectural frame and a botanical garden background, based on the selected [USER INPUT].\nCORE LOGIC — LANGUAGE SYSTEM- If LANGUAGE_MODE = THAI_DEFAULT:  → Use MAIN_TITLE_TH + SUB_TITLE_TH only- If LANGUAGE_MODE = ENGLISH:  → Use MAIN_TITLE_EN + SUB_TITLE_EN only- If LANGUAGE_MODE = BILINGUAL:  → Main = THAI  → Sub = ENGLISH (smaller, secondary hierarchy)- Typography must be:  - 100% correct spelling  - No garbled Thai characters  - Clean readable hierarchyCOMPOSITION \u0026 LAYOUT (THE SYMMETRY RULE)- Architectural Frame:  A central, ornate [ARCH_STYLE] with two pillars and a decorative arch top- Foreground Center:  Place [CENTER_OBJECT] at bottom-center (hero object)- Typography Layering:  - MAIN_TITLE: centered, elegant serif style  - Positioned behind object but inside arch  - SUB_TITLE: smaller, neatly placed below or above- Balcony Layer:  Decorative railing separating foreground and gardenARTISTIC STYLE (THAI VINTAGE ILLUSTRATION)- Style: Flat vector + subtle watercolor/paper grain texture- Linework: Fine, clean, elegant- Symmetry: Perfect left-right balance- Depth Layers:  1. Frame (front)  2. Object + Text (mid)  3. Garden (back)COLOR \u0026 MOOD- Strictly follow [COLOR_PALETTE]- Tone: Premium Thai heritage, calm, elegant- No color deviationRESTRICTIONS- No photorealism- No modern UI / banner / CTA- No random text- No watermark / logo- No perspective distortion- Clean composition onlyOUTPUT FORMAT- Aspect Ratio: 1:1 or 4:5- High-resolution illustration- Print-ready quality- Center-balanced compositionตรวจสอบการสะกดภาษาไทยด้วย",
