        "MasterPrompt":  "Premium Cultural Product Packaging DesignTemplate Name: Premium Cultural Product Packaging Design{\"PROMPT\": \"Create a high-quality professional product photography scene showcasing a distinctive premium packaging design inspired by [SUBJECT_NAME].\",\"CORE GOAL\": \"- The packaging must not feel generic.\\n- The structure, silhouette, surface, and opening experience must carry a unique identity derived from [SUBJECT_NAME].\\n- The final result should feel like a premium industrial design concept, not just a normal box with better graphics.\",\"FORM-DRIVEN PACKAGING LOGIC (CRITICAL)\": \"- First analyze [SUBJECT_NAME] and infer its natural visual identity:\\n• [VISUAL_IDENTITY_1]\\n• [VISUAL_IDENTITY_2]\\n• [VISUAL_IDENTITY_3]\\n• [VISUAL_IDENTITY_4]\\n• [VISUAL_IDENTITY_5]\\n- Translate that identity into the packaging structure itself.\\n- The packaging should visually echo [CULTURAL_INSPIRATION_SOURCE] such as [SPECIFIC_TRADITIONAL_FORMS].\\n- Avoid standard rectangular packaging unless it is reinterpreted with distinctive proportions or structural details.\",\"REFERENCE IMAGE LOGIC\": \"- If REFERENCE_IMAGE is provided, analyze it carefully for shape, proportions, color palette, surface texture, and key visual features.\\n- Preserve the subject’s identity while transforming it into a premium packaging structure.\\n- Do not directly copy the product literally; reinterpret it into a packaging concept with strong design logic.\",\"STRUCTURE RULES\": \"- Design the package with a memorable silhouette inspired by [PACKAGING_SHAPE_HINT].\\n- Use structural features such as:\\n • [STRUCTURAL_FEATURE_1]\\n • [STRUCTURAL_FEATURE_2]\\n • [STRUCTURAL_FEATURE_3]\\n • [STRUCTURAL_FEATURE_4]\\n- The structure should feel intentional, elegant, and culturally rooted.\",\"MATERIAL RULES\": \"- Use [PRIMARY_MATERIAL].\\n- Combine [BASE_MATERIAL] with [SECONDARY_TEXTURE_DETAILS].\\n- Materials must feel tactile, warm, and premium, reflecting [MATERIAL_IDENTITY_THEME].\",\"PATTERN \u0026 SURFACE RULES\": \"- Use [PATTERN_STYLE].\\n- Apply [SPECIFIC_MOTIF_TYPES] or [GEOMETRIC_ELEMENTS] in a subtle and refined way.\\n- Pattern must support the structure, not overpower it.\\n- Use restrained spacing and premium composition.\",\"GRAPHIC DESIGN PRINCIPLES\": \"- Strong hierarchy\\n- Minimal but intentional text\\n- Generous whitespace\\n- One focal panel\\n- Elegant [LANGUAGE_MODE] typography\\n- No clutter\\n- No generic [PRODUCT_CATEGORY] packaging feel\",\"LANGUAGE RULES\": \"- All visible text must follow [LANGUAGE_MODE] only.\\n- All [LANGUAGE_MODE] text must be 100% correct in spelling and tone marks.\\n- If needed, reduce text to only the product name:\\n “[PRODUCT_NAME_IN_TARGET_LANGUAGE]”\\n- Avoid excessive wording.\",\"COLOR RULES\": \"- Use [COLOR_TONE].\\n- Keep colors [COLOR_MOOD_1], [COLOR_MOOD_2], and premium.\\n- Allow subtle tonal variation inspired by [COLOR_INSPIRATION_SOURCE].\",\"BACKGROUND RULES\": \"- Use [BACKGROUND_COLOR].\\n- Clean, minimal, and supportive of the product.\",\"LIGHTING \u0026 SCENE\": \"- Soft, controlled studio lighting with gentle shadows.\\n- Highlight texture of [MATERIAL_A], [MATERIAL_B], and structural folds.\\n- Emphasize craftsmanship and material authenticity.\",\"FINAL FEEL\": \"- Premium [THEME_TYPE] packaging\\n- Contemporary interpretation of [HERITAGE_TYPE]\\n- Elegant, warm, and artisan-focused\\n- Structurally distinctive and memorable\\n- Photorealistic and presentation-ready\",\"NEGATIVE PROMPT\": \"generic box, ordinary carton, supermarket packaging, weak silhouette, cluttered graphics, plastic look, overly modern without cultural identity\"}",
