        "MasterPrompt":  "Traditional Cultural Narrative Mural IllustrationTemplate Name: Traditional Cultural Narrative Mural Illustration{\"art_style\": \"[TRADITIONAL_ART_STYLE] ([NATIVE_NAME])\",\"technical_details\": {\"perspective\": \"Flat, two-dimensional isometric perspective without linear vanishing points.\",\"linework\": \"Intricate and graceful gold or dark outlines ([SPECIFIC_LINE_STYLE]). Stylized [CULTURE] anatomy with elegant, fluid gestures.\",\"shading\": \"Minimal shading; focus on flat color fills and decorative patterns ([SPECIFIC_PATTERN_NAME]).\",\"water_rendering\": \"Stylized rhythmic wavy patterns ([SPECIFIC_ELEMENT_STYLE]) adapted to decorative ground or sky motifs, incorporating [FESTIVAL_OBJECTS], floral patterns, and gentle ornamental swirls instead of water.\"},\"composition\": {\"layout\": \"Dense narrative scene with multiple clusters of people engaging in [CRAFT_OR_ACTIVITY] and [LIFE_THEME], including [SPECIFIC_ACTION_1], [SPECIFIC_ACTION_2], [SPECIFIC_ACTION_3], [SPECIFIC_ACTION_4], and community celebration. Use architectural elements such as [ARCHITECTURAL_STYLE], [STRUCTURE_TYPE_1], [STRUCTURE_TYPE_2], and [STRUCTURE_TYPE_3] to separate different narrative zones within one frame.\",\"narrative\": \"A lively depiction of [LOCATION_NAME] in [REGION], showing the cultural life, craftsmanship, and festive atmosphere of traditional [THEME_SUBJECT] in a serene [ATMOSPHERE_SETTING] setting.\"},\"elements\": {\"characters\": \"People in traditional [ETHNIC_OR_REGIONAL] attire ([SPECIFIC_CLOTHING_ITEMS]) with serene facial expressions. Artisans carefully [ACTION_VERB] and [ACTION_VERB] [KEY_OBJECTS] with delicate [DECORATIVE_MOTIF] motifs. [SECONDARY_CHARACTERS] in [CLOTHING] [ACTION_OR_INTERACTION] with the community.\",\"environment\": \"[ENVIRONMENT_TYPE] landscape with [PLANT_TYPE_1], [PLANT_TYPE_2], [PLANT_TYPE_3], and decorative foliage rendered in traditional clustered leaf patterns. [KEY_OBJECTS] appear throughout the environment—[PLACEMENT_1], [PLACEMENT_2], [PLACEMENT_3]—creating a rhythmic visual harmony.\",\"architecture\": \"Intricately detailed [REGIONAL_ARCHITECTURE_STYLE] houses [STRUCTURAL_DETAIL], open workshop spaces, and [RELIGIOUS_OR_CIVIC_BUILDINGS] with [SPECIFIC_ROOF_STYLE], [ARCHITECTURAL_FINIALS], and decorative elements inspired by traditional [CRAFT_IDENTITY] and [LOCATION_ID] artistic identity.\"},\"color_and_lighting\": {\"palette\": \"Traditional earthy tones dominated by [PRIMARY_COLOR_1], [PRIMARY_COLOR_2], [PRIMARY_COLOR_3], accented with vibrant [OBJECT_NAME] colors such as [ACCENT_COLOR_1], [ACCENT_COLOR_2], [ACCENT_COLOR_3], and [ACCENT_COLOR_4]. Rich use of [METALLIC_TYPE] leaf for highlights, patterns, and ornamental detailing.\",\"atmosphere\": \"Antique, timeless, and culturally rich, resembling a sacred mural that captures the artistic spirit and communal harmony of [CRAFT_OR_TRADITION].\"},\"restrictions\": {\"no_modernity\": \"No modern technology, electricity, or contemporary clothing.\",\"no_photorealism\": \"Avoid 3D depth, realistic lighting, or photographic textures. Must remain a stylized painting.\",\"accuracy\": \"Maintain the integrity of [CULTURAL_DECORATIVE_PATTERNS] and traditional proportions.\"}}",
