        "MasterPrompt":  "Cultural Craft Diorama Macro IllustrationTemplate Name: Cultural Craft Diorama Macro IllustrationBASE_MATERIAL: [GIANT_OBJECT_FRAME] (Giant [OBJECT_DESCRIPTION] fully opened/assembled, showing [STRUCTURAL_DETAIL])SEASON_THEME: [TIME_AND_WEATHER_SETTING]RURAL_SCENE_TYPE: [CULTURAL_ACTIVITY_OR_COMMUNITY_SETTING]HOUSE_STYLE: [REGIONAL_ARCHITECTURE_STYLE] and [SPECIFIC_WORK_AREA]ตั้งอยู่บริเวณ [PLACEMENT_ON_BASE_MATERIAL]FARM_ELEMENTS: [CRAFT_MATERIALS_1], [CRAFT_MATERIALS_2], [TOOLS_AND_EQUIPMENT], [RAW_MATERIALS]WEATHER_DETAILS: [LIGHTING_EFFECTS_THROUGH_MATERIAL], [ATMOSPHERIC_PARTICLES]COLOR_MOOD: [PRIMARY_PALETTE_DESCRIPTION] ตัดกับ [SECONDARY_TONE_DESCRIPTION]Create a highly detailed surreal [THEME_NATION] craft-themed diorama integrated into a giant BASE_MATERIAL, with accurate cinematic composition and strong miniature realism. Strict Rule: No visible text, no titles, and no characters rendered on the image.CORE CONCEPTThe entire miniature world must be built directly on or within the giant BASE_MATERIAL.The BASE_MATERIAL acts as the primary landscape and cultural centerpiece.The focus is entirely on the visual storytelling of [CULTURE_TYPE] handicraft culture through miniature art.MAIN COMPOSITIONCentered or slightly off-center dynamic composition where the BASE_MATERIAL dominates the focus.The scale of the BASE_MATERIAL must feel enormous, with hyper-detailed textures showing [MATERIAL_TEXTURES], joints, and handcrafted structure.The miniature village and craft elements are scaled down significantly to create a sense of wonder.MINIATURE WORLD \u0026 CRAFT ELEMENTSBuild a complete RURAL_SCENE_TYPE directly on the BASE_MATERIAL.Place a HOUSE_STYLE as the focal point of the miniature craft village.Surround the scene with hyper-realistic, tiny FARM_ELEMENTS ([CRAFT_AND_TOOL_SPECIFICS]).Include tiny human figures in traditional [REGIONAL_OR_ETHNIC] attire [ACTION_VERB_1] and [ACTION_VERB_2].All miniature elements must follow the [STRUCTURAL_ALIGNMENT] and physical contours of the BASE_MATERIAL.ATMOSPHERE \u0026 LIGHTINGThe background environment should complement the BASE_MATERIAL (e.g., [BACKGROUND_SETTING_DESCRIPTION]).SEASON_THEME and WEATHER_DETAILS must be visually represented through [LIGHTING_QUALITY], [SHADOW_BEHAVIOR], and floating particles.Use COLOR_MOOD as the master palette for a cinematic, high-end handcrafted aesthetic.TECHNICAL RULESPhotorealistic miniature realism with high-fidelity material textures.Slightly elevated eye-level perspective with a strong bokeh effect on the background.Soft, natural lighting that emphasizes the 3D depth of the diorama.ABSOLUTE RESTRICTION: Do not include any text, letters, or numbers anywhere in the image.No floating objects; everything must be physically grounded.",
        "ExampleImage":  "https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?authuser=0\u0026sz=w800\u0026id=1Di11qYTRri6tPMujiXSdqNxKxZMWDAAd",
        "Application":  "• สำหรับครูผู้สอน: ใช้เป็นสื่อดิจิทัลประกอบนวัตกรรมการเรียนรู้ หรือแผนการสอนที่เน้น Active Learning เพื่อให้นักเรียนสามารถถอดรหัสความคิดสร้างสรรค์จากทุนวัฒนธรรมชุมชนรอบตัวได้   • สำหรับผู้บริหาร: นำโครงสร้างทัศนศิลป์และสไตล์การจัดวางไปใช้ในการออกแบบ Infographic สรุปนโยบายองค์กร หรือทำเป็นภาพประกอบสื่อประชาสัมพันธ์ข่าวสารการพัฒนาคุณภาพการศึกษาของสถานศึกษา"
