        "MasterPrompt":  "Gritty graphic novel illustration using only stark black ink and vivid hot pink/magenta. Features heavy shadows, expressive linework, and a surreal dark gothic aesthetic reminiscent of underground indie comics.Main subject: traditional Bo Sang umbrellas from Northern Thailand, illustrated in an intense semi-abstract comic style. Giant handcrafted paper umbrellas dominate the composition with exaggerated perspective, dramatic bamboo structures, sharp umbrella ribs, torn paper textures, dripping ink details, and swirling ornamental floral patterns distorted into surreal graphic forms.The umbrellas appear inside a mysterious Northern Thai alleyway filled with layered shadows, hanging lanterns, tangled electrical wires, old wooden architecture, and fragmented Lanna decorative motifs. Some umbrellas float unnaturally in the air, partially dissolving into ink splashes, gothic smoke, geometric fragments, and chaotic brush textures.Visual atmosphere should feel:• mysterious• artistic• rebellious• handcrafted• atmospheric• cinematic• culturally surrealUse:• ultra-heavy black shadows• aggressive ink contrast• vivid hot pink/magenta highlights only• rough dry-brush textures• expressive scratchy linework• underground comic energy• distorted perspective• fragmented graphic composition• chaotic negative spaceIncorporate:• traditional Thai floral umbrella patterns• bamboo handle silhouettes• rain-soaked alley reflections• floating paper fragments• abstract smoke trails• ink splatter textures• surreal urban darknessArt style inspired by:• underground indie comics• gothic manga aesthetics• experimental risograph posters• dark editorial illustration• punk graphic novels• handcrafted ink printmakingComposition:dynamic asymmetrical framing with oversized umbrella forms dominating the visual hierarchy. Strong foreground/background separation with layered depth and surreal environmental storytelling.No realistic full-color rendering.No soft pastel tones.No clean commercial polish.No bright cheerful tourism aesthetic.\nOnly:black ink + hot pink/magenta palette, raw graphic energy, expressive shadows, gritty texture, and dark surreal Bo Sang umbrella storytelling.Ultra-detailed, high-contrast graphic novel illustration, handcrafted ink aesthetic, premium underground comic quality, cinematic gothic atmosphere, masterpiece, 8K.",
