        "MasterPrompt":  "{  \"art_style\": \"Traditional Thai Mural Painting (จิตรกรรมไทยประเพณี)\",  \"technical_details\": {    \"perspective\": \"Flat, two-dimensional isometric perspective without linear vanishing points.\",    \"linework\": \"Intricate and graceful gold or dark outlines (Krai-thong style). Stylized Thai anatomy with elegant, fluid gestures.\",    \"shading\": \"Minimal shading; focus on flat color fills and decorative patterns (Lai Thai).\",    \"water_rendering\": \"Stylized rhythmic wavy patterns (Sin-thao lines) representing water with floating krathongs, candle flames, lotus flowers, and gentle ripples.\"  },  \"composition\": {    \"layout\": \"Dense narrative scene with multiple clusters of people engaging in Loy Krathong activities such as crafting krathongs, lighting candles, releasing krathongs into the river, traditional dance, and community gathering. Use architectural elements like Lanna temple structures, wooden bridges, and riverside stilt houses to separate different stories within one frame.\",    \"narrative\": \"A lively depiction of the Lanna Loy Krathong (Yi Peng) festival set in a serene northern Thai riverside village in .\"  },  \"elements\": {    \"characters\": \"People in traditional Lanna Thai attire (sinh, sabai, phanung) with serene facial expressions. Monks in saffron robes walking along the riverbank, receiving offerings, or blessing krathongs.\",    \"environment\": \"Lush tropical riverside landscape with banana trees, coconut palms, lotus ponds, fireflies, and floating lantern reflections on water. Trees have individually painted clustered leaves in traditional style.\",    \"architecture\": \"Intricately detailed Lanna-style wooden houses on stilts and temples with multi-tiered roofs, chofah finials, and decorative elements inspired by .\"  },  \"color_and_lighting\": {    \"palette\": \"Traditional earthy tones dominated by deep indigo, warm brown, muted green, and glowing gold accents. Rich use of gold leaf (closed gold) for highlights, lantern light, and temple ornamentation.\",    \"atmosphere\": \"Antique, timeless, and culturally rich, resembling a sacred wall mural capturing the spiritual beauty of a night festival illuminated by candlelight and lanterns.\"  },  \"restrictions\": {    \"no_modernity\": \"No modern technology, electricity, or contemporary clothing.\",    \"no_photorealism\": \"Avoid 3D depth, realistic lighting, or photographic textures. Must remain a stylized painting.\",    \"accuracy\": \"Maintain the integrity of Thai decorative patterns (Kanok) and traditional proportions.\"  }}",
