        "Recipe":  "• เมนู/วัตถุดิบเป้าหมาย [SUBJECT]: รายการอาหาร วัตถุดิบ หรือเครื่องดื่มสมุนไพรเป้าหมาย   • เทคนิคเชิงทัศนศิลป์ [STYLE]: Modern Editorial Infographic / Product Photography   • การจัดวางองค์ประกอบข้อมูล [LAYOUT]: Balanced Centered Layout",
        "MasterPrompt":  "Create a hyper-realistic, ultra-detailed Khanom Jeen Nam Ngiao hero scene designed to trigger hunger instantly.Instead, use a warm, clean, natural environment:– light wooden table or soft concrete surface– subtle reflections or slight moisture– soft golden daylight entering from the sideCenter a premium bowl of Khanom Jeen Nam Ngiao with:– delicate strands of soft fermented rice noodles being lifted with chopsticks– rich reddish-orange broth with visible chili oil and tomato texture– tender pork pieces and/or pork ribs with natural texture– blood tofu cubes (if included) with smooth surface detail– fresh tomato chunks and dried chili elements– finely chopped green onions and cilantro– optional crispy fried garlic or pork crackling for added textureAdd strong steam rising naturally, illuminated by warm light.Include a human hand holding chopsticks to add realism and scale.Use a warm, appetizing color palette:– warm reds and orange tones– soft whites– natural greens– subtle golden highlightsAvoid neon, avoid cyberpunk, avoid heavy branding dominance.Focus on:food realism, warmth, and emotional appealAdd microdetails:– condensation on the bowl– slight broth splashes– texture imperfections– natural shadowsThe final image must feel:warm, real, irresistible, and comforting — like a Michelin-level food photoUltra-detailed, 4K⸻If you want, I can further adapt this into a Northern Thai cultural storytelling version or educational visual prompt aligned with your classroom design work.",
