        "MasterPrompt":  "Generate a visually engaging bullet-point infographic centered around Thai breakfast: Soy Milk and Chinese Doughnuts (น้ำเต้าหู้ ปาท่องโก๋).Content (เนื้อหา):Main focus includes a warm cup of soy milk (น้ำเต้าหู้) with steam rising, and crispy golden Chinese doughnuts (ปาท่องโก๋) placed beside or dipped into the drink. Include small side elements such as pandan leaves, sesame seeds, or condensed milk.Visual Rules (กฎของการวาด):Use clean line illustrations combined with soft semi-realistic textures. Add arrows or thin pointer lines highlighting key elements (cup, doughnuts, toppings). Composition should be neat and easy to scan.Text Rules (กฎข้อความ):All text in short bullet points using cute, rounded Thai-style typography. Keep sentences concise, friendly, and readable on mobile screens.Caption Rules (กฎคำบรรยาย):Include short labels such as:* “อาหารเช้ายอดนิยม”* “ร้อน หอม อิ่มง่าย”* “จับคู่ลงตัว”* “วิถีสตรีทฟู้ดไทย”Atmosphere (บรรยากาศ):Warm morning street food vibe, soft sunlight, slightly cozy and inviting. Avoid clutter—keep background minimal but suggest a Thai street stall feeling.Style (สไตล์):Modern flat + soft 3D hybrid infographic style, pastel warm tones (cream, light brown, golden yellow), subtle shadows, high clarity, optimized for social media (square 1:1 format).Composition:Centered main subject with evenly spaced bullet points around it. Balanced layout with clear visual hierarchy.Quality:High resolution, sharp focus, clean infographic aesthetic, mobile-first readability.",
