        "MasterPrompt":  "USER_INPUTEVENT_THEME: เทศกาลข้าวเหนียวมะม่วง (Mango Sticky Rice Festival)MASCOTS_AND_ICONS: มะม่วงสุก, ข้าวเหนียวมูน, กะทิ, ช้อน-ส้อม, ใบตอง, จานขนมไทย, ลายหยดกะทิ, ลายเส้นคลื่นหวานCOLOR_PALETTE: Mango Yellow, Coconut Cream White, Leaf GreenGRAPHIC_STYLE: Playful Thai dessert illustration, soft rounded shapes, smooth vector style, cheerful food festival vibeTYPOGRAPHY_VIBE: ฟอนต์ไทยแนวขนมหวาน นุ่มมน สนุก อ่านง่าย คล้ายลายมือเขียนป้ายตลาดLANGUAGE_MODE: ThaiBACKGROUND_COLOR: Coconut Cream Beige⸻PROMPTTASKCreate a professional Event Branding and Spatial Design Assets Presentation Board based on EVENT_THEME.The final image must show a collection of various event design touchpoints arranged systematically like a designer’s portfolio showcase. It must not be a single poster, a single scene, or one isolated logo.⸻LANGUAGE SYSTEM* LANGUAGE_MODE controls all visible text.* If LANGUAGE_MODE = Thai, all visible text must be Thai only.* If LANGUAGE_MODE = English, all visible text must be English only.* If LANGUAGE_MODE = Bilingual, use Thai as the main hierarchy and English as smaller supporting text.* Default language = Thai.* All Thai spelling must be 100% correct.* Do not generate garbled Thai, pseudo-Thai, broken vowels, missing tone marks, or random text.* If accurate Thai rendering is uncertain, reduce secondary text and keep only short main titles.⸻BACKGROUND SYSTEM* Use BACKGROUND_COLOR exactly.* If BACKGROUND_COLOR is empty, default to Pitch Black.* The background must be solid, clean, and non-distracting.* For light backgrounds, ensure assets remain clearly visible with soft contrast.* Do not add environmental scenery behind the board.⸻DESIGN COMPONENTS TO INCLUDEGenerate a matching set of event branding and spatial design assets based on EVENT_THEME.1. Main Key Visual* A horizontal rectangular poster establishing the event theme.* Clearly present “เทศกาลข้าวเหนียวมะม่วง” as the main title.* Showcase mango, sticky rice, coconut cream, and dessert composition visually.2. Entrance Archway / Gate* A structural 2D or 3D cutout design for the event entrance.* Inspired by mango shape, dripping coconut cream, or dessert arch concept.* Must look producible as real event signage.3. Pop-up Booth / Kiosk* A dessert stall design with mango-themed roof, coconut patterns, and playful food graphics.* Include counter, signage, and decorative dessert visuals.4. Photo Booth Frames* Interactive cutout frames with mango mascots, sticky rice elements, speech bubbles like “หวานละมุน” “อร่อยมาก!”* Include dessert-themed shapes and playful food icons.5. Wayfinding \u0026 Props* Direction signs (e.g., “โซนขนมหวาน”, “จุดถ่ายรูป”)* Logo badges, standees, dessert icons, and event markers* Must feel like real printable materials⸻AESTHETIC \u0026 THEME* Follow GRAPHIC_STYLE exactly.* Use cohesive 2D flat vector illustration style.* Soft rounded shapes, smooth edges, friendly proportions.* Cheerful, sweet, dessert-inspired mood.* All assets must look like cohesive printable production files.* MASCOTS_AND_ICONS must appear across multiple assets and interact playfully.⸻COLOR SYSTEM* Strictly follow COLOR_PALETTE.* Mango Yellow = primary highlight* Coconut Cream White = base tone* Leaf Green = natural accent* Colors must feel soft, appetizing, and friendly* Avoid introducing unrelated colors⸻TYPOGRAPHY \u0026 DETAILS* Use TYPOGRAPHY_VIBE for titles and labels* Typography must feel soft, rounded, dessert-like* Add small decorative labels such as “หวาน หอม มัน”, “เทศกาลสุดพิเศษ”* Use speech bubbles where appropriate* Add subtle grid lines or layout guides to enhance presentation feel* Keep text minimal and clean⸻LAYOUT* Multi-asset presentation board layout* Top: event title + key visual* Center: entrance gate + booth (largest elements)* Left: props, standees, dessert signage* Right: photo frames + wayfinding signs* Bottom: badges, icons, arrows, stickers* Maintain spacing and visual balance* Energetic but professionally organized⸻BRAND CONSISTENCY RULE* Every element must belong to the same brand identity* Use consistent mascot style, color palette, typography, and shapes* Avoid inconsistency across assets* The board must feel like one unified design system⸻PRODUCTION FEEL* Assets must look implementable in real event* Clean vector edges* Printable, cuttable, installable structures* Practical proportions⸻STRICT CONSTRAINTS* Do not generate a single scene* Do not generate only one poster* Do not generate only one logo* Do not use unrelated mascots* Do not break brand identity* Do not use photorealism* Do not use painterly style* Do not clutter* Do not generate incorrect Thai text* Do not use wrong background color* Do not add watermark⸻OUTPUT* Single image* Multi-asset event branding presentation board* Solid BACKGROUND_COLOR* Cohesive spatial design system* Professional portfolio quality⸻FINAL INTENTCreate a complete event branding and spatial design assets board where EVENT_THEME becomes a unified visual system across key visual, entrance gate, kiosk, photo frames, wayfinding signs, props, badges, arrows, and character standees.",
