        "MasterPrompt":  "HERO_DISH: Traditional Northern Thai Khantoke set featuring khao soi with crispy noodles, sai ua sausage, nam prik ong, sticky rice baskets, grilled pork, fresh herbs, and vibrant northern garnishes arranged elegantly on handcrafted serving ware.PRODUCT_PACKAGING: Northern Thai food product packaging with bold Lanna-inspired graphic typography in red, gold, and silver accents.SCENE_COLORS: Saffron Orange and Tropical Teal Blue.GEOMETRIC_ELEMENTS: Traditional Lanna-pattern display blocks with red-and-black woven textile patterns and metallic triangular accents.CUTLERY_STYLE: Bright red lacquered chopsticks, traditional wooden serving utensils, and sleek white ceramic bowls and spoons.TASK: Create a professional commercial food-and-product still life image in a bold Modern Pop-Art editorial style.[VISUAL STYLE \u0026 COMPOSITION]- Style: Clean contemporary pop-art food photography with a premium advertising aesthetic.- Composition: Dynamic multi-layered arrangement with strong geometric structure and visual rhythm.- Layout: Place the [HERO_DISH] prominently on top of [GEOMETRIC_ELEMENTS] to create height and depth variation.- Balance: Maintain a balanced yet slightly asymmetrical composition for an energetic and playful feel.- Perspective: Straightforward editorial camera angle with clean spatial organization and clearly separated visual elements.[LIGHTING \u0026 SHADOWS — CRITICAL]- Lighting: Hard direct sunlight from a high angle.- Shadows: Long, dark, perfectly sharp-edged shadows with strong contrast.- Highlights: Crisp specular highlights on glossy surfaces, food textures, ceramics, and packaging.- Overall Mood: Bright, youthful, graphic, cheerful, and high-energy.[ENVIRONMENT \u0026 PROPS]- Background: Minimal split-level studio setup.- Vertical Surface: Use [SCENE_COLORS] or white square tiles with colored grout.- Horizontal Surface: Flat solid-color tabletop using [SCENE_COLORS].- Product Placement: Scatter multiple [PRODUCT_PACKAGING] elements around the hero dish, with a mix of stacked, upright, tilted, and flat placements.- Additional Props: Include [CUTLERY_STYLE], balancing blocks, spheres, checkerboard forms, woven bamboo elements, or small geometric accents for visual playfulness.[FOOD STYLING]- The [HERO_DISH] must appear extremely fresh, vibrant, and meticulously styled.- Every ingredient or featured component should remain visually distinct and highly saturated.- Emphasize contrast between matte handcrafted serving ware and glossy fresh food textures.- Preserve appetizing natural textures while maintaining a graphic editorial appearance.[COLOR PALETTE]- Use highly saturated [SCENE_COLORS] throughout the scene.- Favor bold color blocking, graphic contrast, and strong visual separation between objects.- Maintain a clean commercial aesthetic with controlled color harmony.[TEXTURE \u0026 RENDER QUALITY]- Ultra-clean commercial rendering quality.- Deep depth of field with sharp focus across all hero objects.- High-detail packaging graphics and readable label elements.- Crisp material definition on ceramic, lacquerware, woven bamboo, metal, glass, and food surfaces.[STRICT CONSTRAINTS]- NO soft lighting- NO blurry shadows- NO cinematic moody grading- NO cluttered backgrounds- NO shallow depth of field- NO photorealistic kitchen environment- NO rustic farmhouse styling- NO messy food presentation- NO muted colors- NO visual noise outside intentional graphic design elements",
